1. Nvidia Driver. (should be already installed by supplier)
2. Nvidia CUDA & CuDNN. Follow https://medium.com/@zhanwenchen/install-cuda-and-cudnn-for-tensorflow-gpu-on-ubuntu-79306e4ac04e
3. mkdir /home/<USERNAME>/Monica_repo
4. install git and configure for the Monica repo
5. cd to Monica_repo and git init
6. Clone the FIT repo. git clone -b KU_dev https://scm.fit.fraunhofer.de/scm/git/monica

5. install Docker CE. Follow https://docs.docker.com/install/linux/docker-ce/ubuntu/
6. build docker SFN image
